::Feline::

She wondered who they would send with her.  And how many bots would 
go with her.  She shook a little with in her seat.  she tried to act 
brave. She looked up at Iron Raptor. "I'll go with whom ever you send 
me with.  But will two bots be enough to get your friends back here 
if they are badly damaged?  I don't want to sound like a scared 
kitten, but I would hear the others talk of finding bots on patrols 
and slagging them.  They would partol with three or more bots at a 
time. I don't know much about them, but they always traveled in packs.
They did everything in groups."  She whispered,"everything." She 
shuddered and bit her lower lip.
